<h1>Lua Tooling</h1>

<p>
  The following is a work in progress list of tooling related to Lua. The
  criteria for being included here is that the tool seems fleshed out, and
  also works toward either composition of lua libraries or statically
  compiling an executable. (Instead of embedding in C or another language.)
</p>

<p>
  This may be a living document that's updated over time. Relationships of a
  project to my goals, and the goals themselves, are all subject to change.
</p>

